T*
(1\\) Overview) Tj
T*
(- Project type: Next.js frontend for real-estate lead generation.) Tj
T*
(- Tech stack: Next.js 15, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS.) Tj
T*
(- Hosting model: Static export for S3/CloudFront.) Tj
T*
(- Main goals: Property discovery, lead capture, WhatsApp CTA, SEO.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2\\) Runtime and Build) Tj
T*
(- Dev: npm run dev) Tj
T*
(- Production build: npm run build) Tj
T*
(- Static export enabled in next.config.js \\(output: export\\).) Tj
T*
(- Trailing slash enabled for S3 compatibility.) Tj
T*
(- next/image optimization disabled \\(images.unoptimized = true\\).) Tj
T*
(- Output artifact: frontend/out \\(deploy this folder\\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3\\) Top-level Structure) Tj
T*
(- app/: route tree and layouts \\(App Router\\).) Tj
T*
(  - app/layout.tsx: global metadata, icons, OG, robots defaults.) Tj
T*
(  - app/\\(public\\)/layout.tsx: Header, Footer, WelcomePopup, InquiryModalProvider.) Tj
T*
(  - app/\\(public\\)/* pages: Home, Properties, About, Contact, Privacy, Terms.) Tj
T*
(  - app/\\(admin\\)/* pages: placeholder admin routes \\(noindex from admin layout\\).) Tj
T*
(  - app/robots.ts and app/sitemap.ts: generated SEO endpoints.) Tj
T*
(- components/: reusable UI and feature modules.) Tj
T*
(  - layout/: Header, Footer.) Tj
T*
(  - cards/: PropertyCard, testimonial components.) Tj
T*
(  - forms/: ContactForm lead capture.) Tj
T*
(  - modals/: PropertyInquiryModal, WelcomePopup, provider context.) Tj
T*
(- lib/: shared utilities \\(auth/api constants/emailjs\\).) Tj
T*
(- store/: client stores \\(auth/lead placeholders\\).) Tj
T*
(- public/: static assets \\(hero images, logo, favicon, property media\\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4\\) Routing and Layout Model) Tj
T*
(- Root layout wraps entire app and injects global metadata.) Tj
T*
(- Public layout composes persistent shell for user-facing pages:) Tj
T*
(  Header -> Page Content -> Footer -> Welcome Popup + Inquiry Modal.) Tj
T*
(- Route groups \\(public/admin\\) keep URL clean while separating concerns.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5\\) Data and Component Flow) Tj
T*
(- Home/Properties pages define property arrays \\(mock data currently\\).) Tj
T*
(- PropertyCard receives property props and renders desktop/mobile card UIs.) Tj
T*
(- PropertyCard actions:) Tj
T*
(  - WhatsApp deep link with templated property message.) Tj
T*
(  - Book Site Visit / Call Expert open shared modal via context.) Tj
T*
(- InquiryModalProvider manages modal state globally and injects) Tj
T*
(  PropertyInquiryModal once at layout level.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6\\) Lead Capture Architecture) Tj
T*
